---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/975674309736828928
  Locus:
    Date: 19 Mar 2018
---
The many factors which divide us are actually much more superficial than
those we share. Despite all of the things that differentiate us -- race,
language, religion, gender, wealth and so on -- we are all equal concerning
our fundamental humanity.
